README
=======

Introduction
-------------
delay is a small program that delay during a number of seconds, given by
the first parameter. The program make no effort to delay very accurate.
Primary usage for this program is in crude scripts or CLI when other "sleep"
commands are not available.

Example, delay 2 seconds:
#$ delay 2

Building
---------
Use the Makefile by executing 'make' in a terminal.

#$ make


Installing
-----------

#$ make install

or if you want to specify the install directory:

#$ make install INSTALLDIR=your/dir

Uninstalling
-------------
#$ make uninstall

or if you have specified an install directory:

#$ make uninstall INSTALLDIR=your/dir